It can&#39;t be done without doing a bit of coding to replace the current 
ARCWriterProcessor with one that just drops request/response on disk 
perhaps mirroring the directory layout of the  website being crawled 
taking care to create new local directories if a folder has a million 
files in it.  While such a writer would be an I/O killer, it might make 
Heritrix more accessible; especially for those doing small crawls 
